section.para:
			Quarter Sessions to appoint a Surveyor of the Roads yearly; Notice to Persons appointed.; 
Surveyors to meet to survey ruinous Places, and take Order for repairing the same;
and certify to Quarter Sessions, who are to make Order thereon; Surveyors to require Carts, &c. to work in 	such Places; Surveyors to pay for working beyond limited Time; Two Justices may settle Rate of Payment.
